INSTALLATION
============

  You need Objective Caml.
 
  1. Compile with "make all". It creates a binary file "bibtex2html".

  2. Copy this binary file where you want
     either by editing the Makefile and doing "make install"
     or by copying the file "by hand".

  bibtex2html assumes that "bibtex" is correctly installed and present
  in your path.
